            Reach out to our support team via email at 
            &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;underline underline-offset-2 text-primary &quot;&gt;support@example.com&lt;/a&gt;
            or call 1-800-123-4567.
        &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/RzAccordionSection&gt;
    &lt;RzAccordionSection Title=&quot;What is the refund policy?&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
            Please refer to our &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;underline underline-offset-2 text-primary &quot;&gt;refund policy page&lt;/a&gt; for details.
        &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/RzAccordionSection&gt;
&lt;/RzAccordion&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <!-- Single Open RzAccordion (Only one section open) -->
            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Single Open RzAccordion" class="scroll-mt-20">
                    Single Open RzAccordion
                </RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>
                    In this example, <code>AllowMultipleOpen</code> is set to <code>false</code>, ensuring that only one section is open at a time.
                </RzParagraph>

                <RzBrowser Layout="typeof(PreviewLayout)">
	                <div class="mx-auto p-8 mb-5">
		                <RzAccordion AllowMultipleOpen="false">
			                <RzAccordionSection Title="What browsers are supported?">
				                <p>
					                Our website is optimized for the latest versions of Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge.
					                Check our <a href="#" class="underline underline-offset-2 text-primary ">documentation</a> for more info.
